document_name: http://www.undp.org/content/dam/undp/documents/projects/KEN/Enhanced Effective Information Communications and Technology for Development.docx

outputs.output_descr: The project aims to meet three needs namely, reduce digital gap and promote use of ICT to innovate and spur development, promote responsible journalism and reporting in development and promotion of information access and empowerment for all citizens

project_descr: The project is aimed at bridging the digital divide and spur information access and use for innovation and development in Kenya. It will also seek to enhance capacity and institutionalize professionalism in Information and Communication
